Instead, export the `changeNumber` function directly from the instance, and get a reference to it with [`bind:this`](https://svelte.dev/tutorial/bind-this):

```html
&lt;!-- WastedTime.svelte --&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
	var wastedTime = 0;
	export function changeNumber(){
		console.log(&#39;changing number&#39;)
		wastedTime = 50
	}
&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;Wasted time: {wastedTime}&lt;/h1&gt;
```

```html
&lt;!-- App.svelte --&gt;
&lt;script&gt;
	import { onMount } from &#39;svelte&#39;;
